      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks, while the transmission shifts harshly. The exterior has multiple large dents, significant paint fading, and some rust, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. It is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a parts vehicle.",
