    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows some age, including minor scratches, a few small dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits noticeable wear on the upholstery and carpets from regular use. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it may require some minor maintenance or cosmetic attention in the near future. It\u2019s a solid option for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle that still has plenty of life left.",
