    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a solid value! This car is in fair condition and has served its previous owners well, showing some expected signs of use and character over the years. While it may have some cosmetic wear and minor mechanical needs, it remains a functional and honest vehicle ready for its next chapter. It's a great opportunity to get a reliable set of wheels at a budget-friendly price!",
      "price": 18500.0,
