    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, confirms its status as a premier, as-new acquisition.",
