    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly in incredible shape\u2014looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been kept absolutely spotless. Perfect for someone who wants that brand-new feel without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
